I created a sample GRC dashboard in Excel based on OpenMRS security and compliance metrics. Here’s a breakdown:

| Metric                         | Visualization       | Stakeholder       |
|-------------------------------|---------------------|-------------------|
| HIPAA Compliance %            | Pie Chart           | Exec & Security   |
